						               													<description>La Valse des Masques (The waltz of masks)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;16th century. You are the head of one of the 4 most respected and powerful noble families in Venice. You must use your power to maintain your family's influence and power in the Great Council. The future Doge must be in your favour!  Use every trick in the book and reach the highest levels to rule the Republic of Venice!&amp;#10;Waltz of the Masks is a card game of actions, placements and combinations.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Objective of the game :&amp;#10;The main objective is to have the most influence points, and therefore usually the most &amp;quot;revealed&amp;quot; cards in the highest position, before the end of the game. The higher a &amp;quot;revealed&amp;quot; card is, the more influence value it has for the final count. Thematically, a high card is an advisor who influences the upper echelons of the city.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players play cards in rows and push cards from the bottom row to the top. Cards can be played face up to perform card effects or face down to hide these effects until they come into force later in the game. Players cannot play the same card as the previous player, or the same card as the last player of the previous turn if you are the first player of the turn.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Vous &amp;ecirc;tes &amp;agrave; la t&amp;ecirc;te d&amp;rsquo;une des 4 familles nobles les plus respect&amp;eacute;es et puissantes de Venise. Vous devez user de votre pouvoir afin de conserver l&amp;rsquo;influence et la puissance de votre famille au sein du  Grand Conseil. Le futur Doge doit vous &amp;ecirc;tre favorable! &amp;#10;Usez de toutes les filouteries et atteignez les plus hautes sph&amp;egrave;res afin de r&amp;eacute;gner en ma&amp;icirc;tre sur la R&amp;eacute;publique de Venise!&amp;#10;La Valse des Masques est un jeu de cartes d'actions, de placement et de combinaisons.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Objectif du jeu :&amp;#10;L&amp;rsquo;objectif principal est d&amp;rsquo;avoir le plus de points d&amp;rsquo;influence, et donc en g&amp;eacute;n&amp;eacute;ral le plus de cartes &amp;ldquo;r&amp;eacute;v&amp;eacute;l&amp;eacute;es&amp;rdquo; dans la position la plus haute, avant la fin de la partie.&amp;#10;Plus une carte &amp;ldquo;r&amp;eacute;v&amp;eacute;l&amp;eacute;e&amp;rdquo; est haute, plus elle a de la valeur en influence pour le d&amp;eacute;compte final. Th&amp;eacute;matiquement, une carte haute est un conseiller qui influence les hautes sph&amp;egrave;res de la cit&amp;eacute;.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
